"{\"uid\": \"fiba3x3.com-en-news-2024-3x3-women-defending-champs-usa-break-drought-to-edge-spain-at-paris-olympics.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"1 Aug 2024    PARIS (France) - Defending women's champion USA ignited their Paris Olympics with a tough 17-11 victory over Spain on day three.\\u00c2  With LeBron James watching courtside, emotionally invested for his compatriots, USA breathed life into their campaign after shutting down Spain, who lost for the second time on the day.\\u00c2  After a tight loss earlier in the day to Australia, USA were in a big hole at 0-3 and facing the prospect of an early exit.\\u00c2  \\u00c2\\u00a0The Americans were desperate and they made the fast start with WNBA player Rhyne Howard continuing her hot shooting from deep as the USA had the jump.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7115018654769987, \"rank\": 0.3044837063500404, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999711756152199, \"rank\": 1.6178090254831674e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.7501330347702094, \"rank\": 0.3293115331995178, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBro