sketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhyne_Howard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rhyne Howard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhyne_Howard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhyne_Howard\"}, {\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999711756152199, \"rank\": 1.6178090254831674e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made a tough start in the tournament, Howard settled nicely into her rhythm and made a pretty layup.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"score\": 0.724851907185346, \"rank\": 0.21196400902517382, \"text\": \"Howard\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was also putting effort in on the defensive end, with an emphatic rejection part of a lockdown effort from the USA.\\u00c2  It was time for superstar Hailey Van Lith to cook as she showcased her mesmerizing handles then nailed a two-piece that made a giddy LeBron celebrate enthusiastically in his seat.\\u00c2  Vega Gimeno kept Spain afloat, but Dearica Hamby, like Howard a WNBA player who is building into this tournament, made several big defensive plays before Van Lith nailed the dagger two-piece.\\u00c2  It earned a fist pump from Lebron, who was soon on his feet clapping and acknowledging USA's first win.\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2  Key Player: Howard had early struggles in the tournament, but she's finding her feet and stepped up with a terrific two-way performance.\"